query:
SELECT h.id, h.name, h.linkedDocumentId, d.id as doc_id, d.name as doc_name, d.fileUrl 
FROM hotels h 
INNER JOIN documents d ON h.linkedDocumentId = d.id 
WHERE h.linkedDocumentId IS NOT NULL
LIMIT 30;
